Ideas

Multiple choice quizzes
	Features: timer, calculated score on submit

Memory game (cards are flipped over and you try and make pairs)
	Use: for matching up words and definitions or words and formulas (like acceleration, for example)

Electronic pupil planner
	Features: auto-populates days with class schedule, space to manually write in assignments, space to add a photo instead of typed text (pupils used to take photos of the details of their homework on their phones), calendar that can add test/examination dates and maybe a countdown